extends layout.pug

block mainContent
  p(id="WelcomeMessage") Welcome to #{title}!
  p(id="BusinessIntro").
    Our small business is here to give you the love you need so you can give it to others!
    Whether it be a relaxing time with our home-grown coffee, or the flowers you could give to your loved ones.
    We have everything you need, catering to seasons and climates alike, making sure to give you satisfaction year-round.
    Our doors and hearts are open to have you visit, so come say hello!
  
  table(class="ProductTables")
    thead 
      tr(class="headerrow") 
        th Check Out Our Cafe and Coffeeshop!
        th Check Out our Flowers and Plants Alike!
    tbody 
      tr 
        td 
          p 
            a(href='/CoffeeShop') Coffee Shop and Cafe
          img(
            id="CoffeeShopImage"
            src="/images/CoffeeShopImage.jpg"
          )
        td 
          p 
            a(href='/FlowerShop') Flower Boutique and Lounge 
          img(
            id="FlowerShopImage"
            src="/images/PlantShopImage.jpg"
          )

  br

  div(id="StatisticCharts") 
    canvas(id="quest1Chart")
    br
    canvas(id="quest2Chart")
    br
    canvas(id="quest3Chart")
    